	<text_base_description>Located behind gates in the heart of Nichols Canyon, this exquisite Fred Smathers Mediterranean is the epitome of Old Hollywood and offers the ultimate retreat from city life. Enter through the double doors into a dramatic entryway, complete with soaring ceilings and a grand staircase with hand painted tiles. The eat-in kitchen and formal dining room open to one of many outdoor terraces, perfect for indoor/outdoor entertaining. Descend to the formal living room with highlights including a bar, cozy fireplace, and french doors that open to the outdoor kitchen and sparkling pool and spa. The master suite boasts vaulted ceilings, a balcony, expansive en-suite bathroom and a beautiful private courtyard. Three additional bedroom suites and a spacious office complete the property. This is a prime opportunity to purchase a property rich in privacy, moments from &quot;celebrity row&quot; in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the Hollywood Hills.  </text_base_description>
